### Average predictions

One thing we could ask is what the average prediction for, say, the `fol_class` variable is.
To get that, we can do some tidyverse summarizing on `all_pred`.
This is also called "marginalizing" over all of the other predictors.


::: {#tbl-avg1 .cell tbl-cap='Predictions averaged over `fol_class`'}

```{.r .cell-code}
all_pred |>
 summarise(
   .by = fol_class,
   estimate = mean(estimate)
 ) |>
 arrange(desc(estimate)) |>
 tt()
```

